### Changes Summary

#### about.go Implementation
- Created cobra command with Use, Short, Long, and Run function
- Implemented formatAboutInfo() to detect TTY and route to appropriate formatter
- formatPlainAbout() outputs simple text format with all required info
- formatStyledAbout() uses lipgloss styles:
  - Title style: Bold, pink (205), bottom margin
  - Header style: Bold, cyan (86), top margin
  - Label style: Gray (241), 12 char width
  - Value style: White (255)
  - Link style: Blue (33), underlined
- Displays all required information:
  - Version from internal/version/version.go
  - Platform: GOOS/GOARCH from runtime
  - Go Version from runtime.Version()
  - License: MIT
  - Community links: Discord, Twitter/X, Reddit
  - Repository links: GitHub, Releases

#### about_test.go Implementation
- Uses cobra.Command wrapper with aboutCmd.Run for proper output capture
- All tests create new command, set output buffer, execute, and verify content
- Tests verify presence of all required strings in output
- License test uses strings.ToUpper() for case-insensitive matching

#### root.go Integration
- Registered aboutCmd in init() function alongside other commands
- Positioned after dirsCmd, before updateProvidersCmd

